    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Let's go with a focus on the user experience. But since these are VIP clients, they're used to a certain level of nuance/personalization. I want the guide to explicitly tell them what they might *lose* or what might feel different once the switch happens, so they aren't surprised by any drop in quality. Why don't you start by listing the specific high-touch capabilities you provide that the faster, more automated model might struggle with?",
